  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study addresses the changes in the axonal excitability parameters. It will compare these
      changes in patients with early infantile epileptic encephalopathy with HCN1 channel mutation
      and in control patients, with and without epilepsy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
